00:01:47,380 --> 00:01:50,220
=Episode 21=

3
00:01:52,140 --> 00:01:54,380
(Summer 2012, Beijing)

4
00:01:54,380 --> 00:01:56,510
- Dumbbell is worthless.
- Jingshu is worthless.

5
00:01:59,230 --> 00:02:00,460
Why is Dumbbell worthless?

6
00:02:00,460 --> 00:02:02,260
How is Jingshu worthless?

7
00:02:03,380 --> 00:02:05,260
Jingshu ran away with a rich guy.

8
00:02:05,260 --> 00:02:06,540
Isn't she just a gold-digger?

9
00:02:06,630 --> 00:02:08,230
Dumbbell collected a million

10
00:02:08,230 --> 00:02:09,750
and sold his girlfriend for it.

11
00:02:09,750 --> 00:02:11,140
Is he a good man?

12
00:02:12,790 --> 00:02:14,420
OK, they are both trash.

13
00:02:15,820 --> 00:02:17,470
Why did things turn out this way?

14
00:02:17,470 --> 00:02:19,230
We won't become like them, right?

15
00:02:28,260 --> 00:02:29,260
From now on,

16
00:02:30,380 --> 00:02:31,350
I want to make money.

17
00:02:32,310 --> 00:02:33,790
I want to keep making money.

18
00:02:34,310 --> 00:02:35,580
How much do you want to earn?

19
00:02:38,540 --> 00:02:40,860
I want to have enough
that we can live with dignity.

20
00:02:41,860 --> 00:02:43,540
I want us to have enough to be confident

21
00:02:43,540 --> 00:02:45,030
so that we won't become like them.

22
00:03:02,950 --> 00:03:05,260
Get rich, make a fortune.

23
00:03:05,860 --> 00:03:07,100
Let's get rich.

24
00:03:07,470 --> 00:03:09,380
Let's make a million.

25
00:03:10,540 --> 00:03:11,660
How do we make it?

26
00:03:12,140 --> 00:03:13,660
Whatever Zhaoyang is doing,

27
00:03:13,660 --> 00:03:15,310
we will do it.

28
00:03:17,860 --> 00:03:18,910
Make your move.

29
00:03:20,580 --> 00:03:23,470
The marketing manager
of Fireworks Media,

30
00:03:23,470 --> 00:03:24,950
100 thousand per ad.

31
00:03:27,310 --> 00:03:29,030
The director of Triumph Tourism.

32
00:03:29,030 --> 00:03:31,660
Each travel advertisement costs
10 thousand.

33
00:03:35,140 --> 00:03:36,070
Watch out.

34
00:03:36,100 --> 00:03:38,070
The advertising director of Aohua

35
00:03:38,190 --> 00:03:40,630
and his five minions.

36
00:03:47,260 --> 00:03:49,100
Good cards, but I have

37
00:03:51,790 --> 00:03:53,470
the director of Huge Rock Culture.

38
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:57,040
They need to make music videos for the
dozens of young idols under their name.

39
00:04:02,790 --> 00:04:05,350
Mr. Zhou, you're experienced.

40
00:04:06,190 --> 00:04:06,980
Not at all.

41
00:04:08,140 --> 00:04:09,100
Since that's the case,

42
00:04:10,860 --> 00:04:12,510
Huayi Sisters.

43
00:04:18,700 --> 00:04:19,510
The trump card.

44
00:04:20,430 --> 00:04:21,190
It's my loss.

45
00:04:29,860 --> 00:04:35,310
(Dai Daji)

46
00:04:35,310 --> 00:04:36,460
Hello.

47
00:04:36,580 --> 00:04:39,020
I'm the CEO of
Extraordinary Culture Media,

48
00:04:39,020 --> 00:04:40,430
Dai Daji.

49
00:04:41,430 --> 00:04:42,900
How should I refer you?

50
00:04:43,070 --> 00:04:45,820
I'm a contracted director under
Extraordinary Culture,

51
00:04:45,950 --> 00:04:46,820
Zhou Shui.

52
00:04:47,510 --> 00:04:48,950
Director Zhou.

53
00:04:48,950 --> 00:04:50,020
- Director Zhou.
- Ms. Dai.

54
00:04:50,020 --> 00:04:50,780
I didn't expect

55
00:04:50,990 --> 00:04:53,820
myself to be the only employee
in such a big company.

56
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,310
Do you have a problem with that?

57
00:04:55,310 --> 00:04:56,950
No problem, boss!

58
00:04:57,460 --> 00:04:58,750
Work hard, my staff!

59
00:04:59,020 --> 00:05:00,190
(In 2012,)

60
00:05:00,670 --> 00:05:01,580
(Zhou Shui and I)

61
00:05:01,820 --> 00:05:03,870
(moved back to place
beside the CCTV building.)

62
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:04,840
(Extraordinary Culture)

63
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:06,380
(Under my glorious leadership,)

64
00:05:06,630 --> 00:05:08,430
(Extraordinary Culture Media)

65
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:10,190
(has been in the scene for three years.)

66
00:05:10,340 --> 00:05:12,140
(Commercial Advertisement Contract)

67
00:05:12,430 --> 00:05:14,110
This is our first contract.

68
00:05:14,110 --> 00:05:14,700
That's right.

69
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:16,920
If there is a first,
there will be a second.

70
00:05:18,430 --> 00:05:20,140
We're going to get a house and a car.

71
00:05:20,140 --> 00:05:21,820
A house and a car!

72
00:05:21,870 --> 00:05:24,220
We're going to be rich!

73
00:05:28,580 --> 00:05:32,060
(Summer 2016, Beijing)

74
00:05:32,670 --> 00:05:33,510
I know.

75
00:05:33,700 --> 00:05:35,670
Our filming is completed for sure.

76
00:05:35,670 --> 00:05:36,580
Shouldn't you settle

77
00:05:36,580 --> 00:05:37,950
the final payment?

78
00:05:38,070 --> 00:05:39,990
You've been on the phone all the way.

79
00:05:40,550 --> 00:05:41,580
Okay, I got it.

80
00:05:41,580 --> 00:05:42,340
Understood.

81
00:05:42,380 --> 00:05:44,000
I'll get back to you later.
I have to go.

82
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:44,760
Your mother is here

83
00:05:44,760 --> 00:05:46,550
and you can't even accompany her
for a moment?

84
00:05:46,550 --> 00:05:48,760
You didn't say a single word to me.
Always on your phone.

85
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:50,630
How did I not accompany you?
Am I not here?

86
00:05:50,630 --> 00:05:51,190
Walk quickly.

87
00:05:51,190 --> 00:05:53,950
I'm talking about Zhou Shui.
His mother-in-law is here in Beijing.

88
00:05:53,950 --> 00:05:55,140
Did he care about me?

89
00:05:55,550 --> 00:05:58,190
Three strikes and he's out.
He has missed his appearance twice.

90
00:05:58,190 --> 00:05:59,310
Figure it out yourself.

91
00:05:59,750 --> 00:06:00,260
Okay.

92
00:06:00,380 --> 00:06:01,780
You're both busy all the time.

93
00:06:01,780 --> 00:06:02,870
Your eyes are full of money

94
00:06:02,870 --> 00:06:04,340
but I don't see you making a penny.

95
00:06:04,550 --> 00:06:06,460
Where's the money?
Have you got me money yet?

96
00:06:12,990 --> 00:06:13,750
What's this?

97
00:06:14,070 --> 00:06:15,990
What's this? My car.

98
00:06:17,580 --> 00:06:18,380
Mercedes?

99
00:06:18,550 --> 00:06:19,340
Mercedes.

100
00:06:20,950 --> 00:06:21,700
You bought it?

101
00:06:22,340 --> 00:06:23,520
Of course.

102
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:24,580
You rented it, didn't you?

103
00:06:24,990 --> 00:06:26,340
I bought it in full.

104
00:06:27,510 --> 00:06:28,510
Oh my God.

105
00:06:29,960 --> 00:06:31,750
- Isn't it beautiful?
- Did you really buy it?

106
00:06:31,750 --> 00:06:32,870
I bought it.

107
00:06:36,580 --> 00:06:37,700
You're good.

108
00:06:40,430 --> 00:06:42,000
Mrs. Dai. Hi, Mrs. Dai.

109
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:42,580
Hi, Mrs. Dai.

110
00:06:43,200 --> 00:06:43,600
Zhou Shui.

111
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:44,670
Mrs. Dai, please come in.

112
00:06:44,670 --> 00:06:45,550
Long time no see.

113
00:06:45,550 --> 00:06:46,430
Long time no see.

114
00:06:46,430 --> 00:06:47,820
Come on, let me handle the luggage.

115
00:06:48,140 --> 00:06:49,510
Should I change my shoes?

116
00:06:49,510 --> 00:06:50,360
No, it's fine.

117
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:52,220
Someone will come to clean up
in the afternoon.

118
00:06:52,220 --> 00:06:53,200
Yes, we hired a cleaner.

119
00:06:53,430 --> 00:06:56,140
Welcome, Mrs. Dai. Come in, please.

120
00:06:57,700 --> 00:06:58,670
It looks really nice.

121
00:06:58,750 --> 00:06:59,000
Right?

122
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:01,670
After not seeing you for some time,
you've become better at talking.

123
00:07:01,670 --> 00:07:03,870
All these skills were
honed from buttering up clients.

124
00:07:04,700 --> 00:07:07,190
Large floor-to-ceiling windows.
Great view.

125
00:07:07,780 --> 00:07:08,950
Right in the city ​​center.

126
00:07:09,510 --> 00:07:10,870
High floor, how does it look?

127
00:07:10,990 --> 00:07:12,580
Very good. It must be expensive, right?

128
00:07:12,820 --> 00:07:13,630
Is it expensive?

129
00:07:13,900 --> 00:07:16,020
To our Director Zhou, it's just...

130
00:07:16,020 --> 00:07:16,820
It's nothing.

131
00:07:16,820 --> 00:07:18,020
Nothing much.

132
00:07:19,110 --> 00:07:21,430
Buy whatever you want.

133
00:07:21,430 --> 00:07:21,920
Okay?

134
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,440
Yes, just shop as you please, Mrs. Dai.

135
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:24,920
You've really made a fortune, huh?

136
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:27,070
No, not really.
Anyway, we can afford these things.

137
00:07:27,070 --> 00:07:28,140
Shui will pay the bill.

138
00:07:28,460 --> 00:07:29,190
I'll pay the bill.

139
00:07:29,190 --> 00:07:30,430
Isn't it expensive in the mall?

140
00:07:30,430 --> 00:07:32,000
- It's okay.
- Shall we have a look there?

141
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:32,190
Look.

142
00:07:32,340 --> 00:07:33,630
No, it's too expensive.

143
00:07:33,630 --> 00:07:34,820
It's okay, just take a look.

144
00:07:35,310 --> 00:07:35,880
This one.

145
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:36,670
Isn't it beautiful?

146
00:07:36,670 --> 00:07:37,820
It's gorgeous.

147
00:07:37,960 --> 00:07:40,880
Let's take a look inside, Mrs. Dai.
It's okay, there are handbags in there.

148
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:41,820
Hold on, Zhou Shui.

149
00:07:42,670 --> 00:07:44,990
I forgot that we have a conference call
this afternoon.

150
00:07:45,310 --> 00:07:46,080
Did you forget too?

151
00:07:46,080 --> 00:07:47,950
Yes. We need to have
a phone call with Mr. Li.

152
00:07:47,950 --> 00:07:48,510
Yes.

153
00:07:48,510 --> 00:07:49,760
Let's leave then.

154
00:07:49,760 --> 00:07:51,430
- You just go shopping.
- Just wait for us.

155
00:07:51,430 --> 00:07:52,260
- Wait for us.
- Yeah.

156
00:07:52,260 --> 00:07:53,600
We'll be back right after the call.

157
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:54,800
- Just a minute, Mrs. Dai.
- Yes.

158
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:55,760
Okay, you guys get busy.

159
00:07:55,760 --> 00:07:56,020
Go on.

160
00:07:56,310 --> 00:07:57,780
Mr. Li.

161
00:07:58,310 --> 00:07:59,340
I'm sorry.

162
00:08:07,110 --> 00:08:09,900
Excuse me. This is our exhibit.
Please do not touch it with your hands.

163
00:08:11,190 --> 00:08:13,700
I just want to see what material it is.

164
00:08:14,260 --> 00:08:15,630
This is a lambskin handbag.

165
00:08:15,630 --> 00:08:16,780
It's 30 thousand.

166
00:08:16,990 --> 00:08:17,700
How much?

167
00:08:17,700 --> 00:08:18,430
30 thousand.

168
00:08:18,900 --> 00:08:19,580
30...

169
00:08:20,460 --> 00:08:21,670
This bag looks pretty nice.

170
00:08:22,310 --> 00:08:23,670
Of course, it's so expensive.

171
00:08:23,820 --> 00:08:24,700
Bag it up.

172
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:28,070
Miss, you have a really good taste.
I'll pack it up right away.

173
00:08:28,070 --> 00:08:28,990
I don't want it.

174
00:08:28,990 --> 00:08:30,070
I've just touched it once.

175
00:08:30,070 --> 00:08:31,560
You can't just force a deal like this!

176
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:33,270
Mrs. Dai, consider it a gift.

177
00:08:36,620 --> 00:08:38,550
I've tasted so many meals you made.

178
00:08:39,190 --> 00:08:41,270
This is my thank-you gift to you.

179
00:08:45,790 --> 00:08:46,620
Oh, you are...

180
00:08:46,860 --> 00:08:47,620
Jingshu.

181
00:08:51,980 --> 00:08:53,030
It really is you.

182
00:08:59,270 --> 00:09:01,270
I've got 58 likes on this post.

183
00:09:01,460 --> 00:09:02,220
That's great.

184
00:09:02,220 --> 00:09:02,440
Nice.

185
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:04,160
Zhou Shui.
Take a few more photos for me here.

186
00:09:04,160 --> 00:09:04,910
- Jingshu.
- Okay.

187
00:09:05,100 --> 00:09:06,670
Let's add each other on WeChat.

188
00:09:06,670 --> 00:09:07,310
Yes.

189
00:09:07,430 --> 00:09:09,390
I have stopped using my QQ
for a long time now.

190
00:09:09,390 --> 00:09:10,150
I'll scan yours.

191
00:09:11,270 --> 00:09:12,620
Okay.

192
00:09:12,790 --> 00:09:13,440
Jiji.

193
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,560
- Alright, here we go.
- Okay.

194
00:09:14,560 --> 00:09:15,880
We're in touch now.

195
00:09:15,880 --> 00:09:17,390
(Movie poet, Tarkovsky.)
So beautiful.

196
00:09:18,950 --> 00:09:19,580
Wow, Daji.

197
00:09:19,580 --> 00:09:21,270
You're a total career woman now.

198
00:09:22,030 --> 00:09:24,980
Not really. I'm just
promoting my company.

199
00:09:25,790 --> 00:09:26,700
Maintaining our image.

200
00:09:27,430 --> 00:09:29,640
What are you doing?
I won't take your money.

201
00:09:29,640 --> 00:09:31,430
No, you have to take the money
for the handbag.

202
00:09:31,430 --> 00:09:31,840
No way.

203
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:33,400
- Jingshu.
- Seriously. This...

204
00:09:33,950 --> 00:09:34,670
Just accept it.

205
00:09:34,670 --> 00:09:36,220
I can still afford a handbag.

206
00:09:36,220 --> 00:09:38,100
It's not about the money, come on.

207
00:09:38,220 --> 00:09:39,820
This is my gift to Mrs. Dai.

208
00:09:39,860 --> 00:09:42,150
I should be the one gifting her.

209
00:09:42,220 --> 00:09:43,740
Why are you two so distant from me?

210
00:09:44,790 --> 00:09:46,340
Do you guys dislike my money?

211
00:09:49,740 --> 00:09:50,340
Jingshu.

212
00:09:50,910 --> 00:09:53,190
I've finished taking pictures

213
00:09:53,190 --> 00:09:54,620
and flaunting it.

214
00:09:54,620 --> 00:09:55,550
This handbag...

215
00:09:55,910 --> 00:09:57,670
Mrs. Dai, this is a gift to you.

216
00:09:57,670 --> 00:09:59,340
I've eaten so many meals that you cooked.

217
00:09:59,340 --> 00:10:00,160
Are you kidding me?

218
00:10:00,160 --> 00:10:01,950
How can those meals
be worth 30 thousand yuan?

219
00:10:01,950 --> 00:10:03,760
How can I make such expensive meals?

220
00:10:03,760 --> 00:10:05,360
30 thousand yuan is just a small amount.

221
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:07,550
Jingshu, please accept it.

222
00:10:08,500 --> 00:10:09,190
All right.

223
00:10:09,190 --> 00:10:12,100
Jingshu, how did you come today?
We drove here, we can give you a ride.

224
00:10:12,430 --> 00:10:13,430
No, my ride is here.

225
00:10:19,030 --> 00:10:20,190
I'll take my leave then.

226
00:10:20,580 --> 00:10:21,340
Bye-Bye.

227
00:10:21,670 --> 00:10:22,460
Bye-Bye.

228
00:10:24,030 --> 00:10:25,910
Daji, let's meet up soon.

229
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:27,310
Bye, Mrs. Dai.

230
00:10:27,310 --> 00:10:27,910
Bye, Shui.

231
00:10:27,910 --> 00:10:28,620
Bye-Bye.

232
00:10:32,950 --> 00:10:34,700
What's wrong?

233
00:10:34,700 --> 00:10:36,460
Is her car very expensive?

234
00:10:37,820 --> 00:10:39,980
It's only ten times more expensive
than our car.

235
00:10:39,980 --> 00:10:40,820
About that.

236
00:10:40,980 --> 00:10:41,680
- What?
- Let's go.

237
00:10:41,680 --> 00:10:43,200
- Let's go home.
- Don't think about it.

238
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:43,580
Let's go.

239
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:53,790
Thank you for your hard work.

240
00:10:56,500 --> 00:10:57,460
What do you mean?

241
00:10:58,150 --> 00:10:59,070
These few days,

242
00:10:59,670 --> 00:11:02,030
you've been trying to make my mom happy
in different ways.

243
00:11:05,340 --> 00:11:06,860
This is just the beginning.

244
00:11:08,620 --> 00:11:10,580
I promised your mother that
I would make you happy.

245
00:11:12,030 --> 00:11:13,700
We're going to be happier and happier.

246
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:16,200
That way, your mother will also
become happier.

247
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:19,860
What about you? Are you happy?

248
00:11:20,100 --> 00:11:20,980
I'm happy.

249
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:22,790
I will be happy if you are happy.

250
00:11:25,580 --> 00:11:26,620
I'm very happy.

251
00:11:29,100 --> 00:11:29,910
Working overtime.

252
00:11:32,190 --> 00:11:32,980
Overtime!

253
00:11:49,400 --> 00:11:51,100
Hey, goddess.
What are you looking at there?

254
00:11:54,620 --> 00:11:56,910
What's so good about this flower?

255
00:11:57,390 --> 00:11:59,270
- Sleep now. What time is it?
- I'm happy.

256
00:11:59,790 --> 00:12:00,580
Are you happy?

257
00:12:01,580 --> 00:12:03,670
How are you doing today?
You look very happy.

258
00:12:04,030 --> 00:12:05,310
Didn't I tell you?

259
00:12:06,070 --> 00:12:08,220
Poor couples are sad.

260
00:12:08,390 --> 00:12:09,550
He's making money now.

261
00:12:09,550 --> 00:12:11,120
You two don't even argue anymore,
do you?

262
00:12:12,030 --> 00:12:12,500
Yes.

263
00:12:13,190 --> 00:12:15,070
Then can you stop worrying now?

264
00:12:15,550 --> 00:12:18,030
He fulfilled all his promises.

265
00:12:20,070 --> 00:12:20,980
Not yet.

266
00:12:21,620 --> 00:12:23,270
Why do you say so?

267
00:12:28,550 --> 00:12:29,190
Mom,

268
00:12:29,310 --> 00:12:32,190
You went shopping from Wangfujing
to Tongzhou.

269
00:12:32,790 --> 00:12:34,580
I can't believe I fell for your trick.

270
00:12:35,190 --> 00:12:36,190
It's on the way.

271
00:12:37,720 --> 00:12:39,550
There are drinks and
air conditioning in here.

272
00:12:39,550 --> 00:12:41,600
It's better than getting scorched
by the sun outside.

273
00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:42,790
Yes, let's take a look here.

274
00:12:42,790 --> 00:12:44,030
This is our sky garden.

275
00:12:44,030 --> 00:12:44,670
